precis:
Amendments to the DESIGNATED PROVISIONS REGULATIONS which designate those
provisions of the "TRANSITION TO CHAPTER 3 AEROPLANES ORDER" which may be
enforced by means of an administrative monetary penalty and establish the
maximum fines payable by individuals or corporations.
